OL,3,CMan who killed his mother sentenced to
OL,4,C21 years in jail
OL,6,FA man who killed his mother has been
OL,7,Fsentenced to life imprisonment to
OL,8,Fserve a minimum of 21 years.
OL,10,FDuring the evening of Sunday 11 May
OL,11,Fthis year, officers were called to
OL,12,FBiddle Road in Littlethorpe, where 72-
OL,13,Fyear-old Ellen Cook was found
OL,14,Fseriously injured.
OL,16,FMrs Cook had suffered multiple stab
OL,17,Fwounds and died at the scene.
OL,19,FWitnesses identified her son Daniel
OL,20,FCook as the man who attacked Mrs Cook.
