OL,6,FWhen officers arrived at the family
OL,7,Fhome in Biddle Road, they were
OL,8,Fconfronted by 39-year-old Daniel, who
OL,9,Fwas carrying a knife and wouldn't co-
OL,10,Foperate.
OL,12,FHe pleaded guilty to manslaughter on
OL,13,Fthe basis of diminished responsibility.
