OL,3,CMan who killed his mother sentenced to
OL,4,C21 years in jail
OL,6,FDaniel, formerly of Atkinson Road,
OL,7,FAshby, was sentenced today (Friday 12
OL,8,FDecember) to a hybrid sentence with a
OL,9,Fhospital order, which means Cook will
OL,10,Fserve the first part of his sentence
OL,11,Fin a secure hospital and be
OL,12,Ftransferred to prison to complete his
OL,13,Fsentence when deemed to be well enough.
