OL,3,CMan who killed his mother sentenced to
OL,4,C21 years in jail
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Mark Sinski,
OL,7,Ffrom the East Midlands Special
OL,8,FOperations Unit Murder Investigation
OL,9,FTeam, said: "This was a horrific
OL,10,Fincident with very tragic and
OL,11,Fheartbreaking consequences. A family
OL,12,Fhas been left utterly devastated by
OL,13,Fthe events of that evening.
OL,15,F"The family of Mrs Cook have shown
OL,16,Fimmense bravery throughout the
OL,17,Finvestigation and subsequent criminal
OL,18,Fproceedings and my thoughts continue
OL,19,Fto remain with them at this most
OL,20,Fdifficult time.
