OL,6,F"A number of witnesses assisted at the
OL,7,Fscene at the time of the incident to
OL,8,Ftry and help Mrs Cook and also
OL,9,Fprovided statements to assist our
OL,10,Fenquiries that followed ` I would like
OL,11,Fto thank these witnesses for your
OL,12,Fsupport throughout as we worked to
OL,13,Ffind answers for Mrs Cook's family.
OL,14,FThank you."
